"{\n  \"text\": \"The wood on my raised bed was rotting and needed to be replaced. And with this job, I was a little bit more intimidated by it because there was a lot of extra structure that I had to take down that I'd attached to the uh bed as the brace. All this needed to come off and needed to be reattached to the new bed. And I was a little bit bothered and worried about that, but it turned out pretty well. Um I had to dig out a lot of the ground in order to get these boards level because there was a lot of overgrown stuff and the the bed kind of piled out of there when I was putting it in there to me shoveling it back in. But it all went in and the cross the trellis uh works in and I had to reattach everything here. But then uh the fence that goes around it also needed to be attached, and that was a little bit of a problem, it wasn't sturdy, so I created I put in a little crossbar there that attaches to the bed, and it turned out pretty well. I was happy with the sturdiness of it all. And uh this is kind of the finished job here. Uh you'll see it looks pretty good. There's a little gap where the soil needs to meet the wall around the edges. You'll see it right here. And I'm gonna fill this in, it'll be good again.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" The wood on my raised bed was rotting and needed to be replaced.\",\n      \"start\": 0.24,\n      \"end\": 3.04,\n      \"duration\": 2.8,\n      \"confidence\": 0.994,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" The\",\n          \"start\": 0.24,\n          \"end\": 0.4,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 0.997\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" wo\",\n          \"start\": 0.4,\n          \"end\": 0.48,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"od\",\n          \"start\": 0.48,\n          \"end\": 0.64,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n